          {
            "title": "Aggregate functions",
            "id": 96481,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Les opérations comme <code>MIN</code> et <code>MAX</code> sont appelées <strong>fonctions d'agrégation</strong> car elles renvoient un seul résultat.</p><database visible-if=\"always\" bootstrapScript=\"CREATE TABLE ticket (&#xA; museum varchar(255),&#xA; price numeric(2,1)&#xA;);&#xA;&#xA;INSERT INTO ticket (museum, price)&#xA;VALUES ('Louvre', 17);&#xA;&#xA;INSERT INTO ticket (museum, price)&#xA;VALUES ('Petit Palais', 0);&#xA;&#xA;INSERT INTO ticket (museum, price)&#xA;VALUES ('Centre Pompidou', 14);&#xA;&#xA;INSERT INTO ticket (museum, price)&#xA;VALUES ('Musée Rodin', 9);&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;\"><tables><table name=\"ticket\"><row><header content=\"museum\" /><header content=\"price\" /></row><row><data content=\"Louvre\" /><data content=\"17\" /></row><row><data content=\"Petit Palais\" /><data content=\"0\" /></row><row><data content=\"Centre Pompidou\" /><data content=\"14\" /></row><row><data content=\"Musée Rodin\" /><data content=\"9\" /></row></table></tables></database><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"sql\" name=\"script.sql\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"SELECT\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"MIN\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(price)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"FROM\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" ticket;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"7\" endIndex=\"17\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"price\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><table name=\"Result\"><row><header content=\"MIN(price)\" /></row><row><data content=\"0\" /></row></table></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>MIN(price)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Aliasing",
            "id": 96482,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nous pouvons utiliser un alias pour renommer le résultat. Ici, nous renommons <code>MIN(price)</code> en <code>cheapest</code>.</p><database visible-if=\"always\" bootstrapScript=\"CREATE TABLE ticket (&#xA; museum varchar(255),&#xA; price numeric(2,1)&#xA;);&#xA;&#xA;INSERT INTO ticket (museum, price)&#xA;VALUES ('Louvre', 17);&#xA;&#xA;INSERT INTO ticket (museum, price)&#xA;VALUES ('Petit Palais', 0);&#xA;&#xA;INSERT INTO ticket (museum, price)&#xA;VALUES ('Centre Pompidou', 14);&#xA;&#xA;INSERT INTO ticket (museum, price)&#xA;VALUES ('Musée Rodin', 9);&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;\"><tables><table name=\"ticket\"><row><header content=\"museum\" /><header content=\"price\" /></row><row><data content=\"Louvre\" /><data content=\"17\" /></row><row><data content=\"Petit Palais\" /><data content=\"0\" /></row><row><data content=\"Centre Pompidou\" /><data content=\"14\" /></row><row><data content=\"Musée Rodin\" /><data content=\"9\" /></row></table></tables></database><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"sql\" name=\"script.sql\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"SELECT\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"MIN\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\"(price) \" /><text value=\"AS\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" cheapest\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"FROM\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" ticket;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"18\" endIndex=\"20\" /><option startIndex=\"21\" endIndex=\"29\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"most_expensive\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><table name=\"Result\"><row><header content=\"cheapest\" /></row><row><data content=\"0\" /></row></table></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Assurez-vous de choisir <code>AS</code> suivi de <code>cheapest</code>.</p></body></html>"
